				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/C%E1%BA%A5p-giang-ti%C3%AAn-tr%C3%A0/poem-q8346Hj_4cF4MP4KzsKlew">Cấp giang tiên trà - 汲江煎茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/D%C4%A9nh-Ch%C3%A2u-l%C3%A3o-%C3%B4ng-ca/poem-sMaN29nfwosLLi7BpB4dYg">Dĩnh Châu lão ông ca - 穎州老翁歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/author-0SVWGWsIUnN7yr-6nBm82Q">Nạp Tân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-vi%C3%AAn-l%E1%BA%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-sjhsILPCdxzCpHtqaPH6cg">Điền viên lạc kỳ 5 - 田園樂其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Pha-b%C3%A1t-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-tSQhIYw_8UwKcORa8K_Zmg">Đông Pha bát thủ kỳ 2 - 東坡八首其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C3%B4-ng%C5%A9-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tham-m%C6%B0u-C%E1%BB%A9/poem-p42Y4_JJGaYn8YKIGjyPrQ">Phụng tặng Lô ngũ trượng tham mưu Cứ - 奉贈盧五丈參謀琚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/T%C3%A2y-S%C6%A1n-t%E1%BA%A7m-T%C3%A2n-Ng%E1%BA%A1c/poem--eKGa0b9xvttt-a0SDyPcA">Tây Sơn tầm Tân Ngạc - 西山尋辛諤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/author-ep8IiRc7UH2qX75S-LVnLw">Mạnh Hạo Nhiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ph%C3%B3-khuy%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-Quan-d%E1%BB%8Bch-l%C3%A2u/poem-hY8PNQORtKxlM1uGu3FtlQ">Thu nhật phó khuyết đề Đồng Quan dịch lâu - 秋日赴闕題潼關驛樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/T%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BA%BF-v%C4%83n/poem-eH6-j7g098C-j3cSVlJ0sg">Tự tế văn - 自祭文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-li%C3%AAn-c%C3%BA-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-b%C3%A0i-lu%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1n-nh%E1%BB%8B-ti%C3%AAu-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-wMQlYGlF6aUupM2pBicmdQ">Tức cảnh liên cú ngũ ngôn bài luật nhất thủ, hạn “nhị tiêu” vận - 即景聯句五言排律一首，限二蕭韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/%E1%BB%A8c-Trung-d%C5%A9ng-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%C3%B3-%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-T%C3%B4n-%C4%90%C3%A0i-h%E1%BB%93i-thi-tr%C3%ACnh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-PqSwvT4-WTN5Y1giD7HeKg">Ức Trung dũng Thiếu phó Đặng Tôn Đài, hồi thi trình thướng kỳ 2 - 憶中勇少傅鄧尊台，回詩呈上其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
